1) Raises your chance to gain skill in your craft 5%.  Not sure on the effectiveness of this one.  Gained skill 2 out of 3 tries on a blue con item.  This item wears out after 10 tries.  Its charged so im not certain as to whether it can recharged at this time, be interesting to try as a bug test.<br>
<br>
2) Raises the speed at which you craft some amount, didn't get this one yet... gonna try it next time.<br>
<br>
3) Raises the quality on your items you craft, I REALLY want to try this one out.<br>
<br>
The Herald implied there would be a cap on the number of times one could complete the quest, however the in game dialogue implies that you could do the quest a number of times, possibly indefinately.  Not sure how the coding will go.<br>
<br>
If you guys have any questions for me just post them here and I will see if I can answer them... as I get more information I will update. <p>Lanval Cadarn<br>
